Long Point Offshore Fund Form D
The Massachusetts-based Long Point Offshore Fund Ltd filed FormD for $9.88 million offering. The date of first sale was 2005-04-01. The raised $9.88 million. The offering is still open. The total offering amount was $9.88 million. The offering form was filed on 2015-12-11. Long Point Offshore Fund Ltd’s clarification was: The total amount sold and the number of investors disclosed in this Form D reflect only sales to US investors and do not take redemptions and/or withdrawals into consideration.. 
 Long Point Offshore Fund is based in Massachusetts. The filler’s business is Pooled Investment Fund. The D form was submitted by Richard W Silver Director of the Issuer. The company was incorporated more than five years ago. The filler’s address is: C/O Elian Fiduciary Services (Bvi) Ltd., Nemours Chambers, Po Box 3170, Roadtown, Tortola, British Virgin Isle., D8, Virgin Islands, British, 00000. D/B/A Mad River Investors Mrm-Horizon Advisors, Llc is the related person in the form and it has address: 84 State Street, Suite 800, Boston, Ma, Massachusetts, 02109. Link to Long Point Offshore Fund Filing: 000114036115044439.
Analysis of Long Point Offshore Fund Offering
On average, companies in the Pooled Investment Fund sector, sell 37.80 % pooled investment interest. Long Point Offshore Fund sold 100.00 % of the offering. The average investment floor size is $24.76 million for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund industry sector. The total amount raised is 60.08 % smaller than the average for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund sector. 

